---
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
---

<BlogLayout 
  title="Authority Guides - Savor"
  description="In-depth guides on food rating methodology, AI technology, and expert tips from the Savor team."
>
  <div class="mb-12 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Authority Guides</h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600">Learn our rating philosophy, AI accuracy and pro tips in these in-depth articles.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <a href="/how-our-10-point-scale-works" class="group block p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-600">Inside Savor's 10 Point Food Scoring System</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">A transparent look at the criteria, maths and tasting discipline behind Savor's dish ratings so you can trust every number you see.</p>
      <span class="text-orange-600 font-semibold">Read Guide →</span>
    </a>

    <a href="/how-to-track-every-fried-chicken-youve-eaten" class="group block p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-600">How to Track Every Fried Chicken You've Ever Eaten Without a Spreadsheet</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">A step by step guide to building a personal fried chicken database with Savor.</p>
      <span class="text-orange-600 font-semibold">Read Guide →</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 text-center">
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-4">More authority guides coming soon...</p>
    <a href="/blog" class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 transition">← Back to Knowledge Hub</a>
  </div>
</BlogLayout> 